title: Ordinance to block Arlington at Clemens Place

abstracts.abstract: BOARD BILL NO. 191  INTRODUCED BY ALDERMAN FRANK WILLIAMSON An Ordinance directing the Director of Streets to temporarily close, barricade, or otherwise impede the flow of traffic on Arlington Avenue at Clemens Place at a part of 300 feet north of Enright Avenue and the northeast corner of Arlington Avenue to the northwest corner of Arlington Avenue and containing an emergency clause.
